text: Jacob Hergenhahn (November 12, 1881 - May 20, 1966) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1966 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ludwigshafen
